items.name: Berries Summer Cupcakes
items.description: Delight in the season with our Berries Summer Cupcakes. Bursting with juicy flavors, these treats are a summer sensation.

items.name: Brownies Different Flavor
items.description: Indulge in our diverse Brownies Collection, offering a spectrum of flavors. Elevate your taste journey with every delectable bite.

items.name: Butter Cookies
items.description: Melt-in-your-mouth Butter Cookies, a symphony of richness and delicate texture. Elevate your tea time or any occasion with these delights.

items.name: Cherry Jelly Cheesecake
items.description: Savor the blend of smooth cheesecake and vibrant cherry jelly. A luscious dessert that harmonizes creamy indulgence with fruity delight.

items.name: Chocolate Blueberries Cake
items.description: Experience decadence with our Chocolate Blueberries Cake. Rich chocolate meets bursts of tangy blueberries for a delightful and indulgent treat.

items.name: Chocolate Bonbons
items.description: Indulge in exquisite Chocolate Bonbons. Each bite-sized masterpiece offers a symphony of flavors, making moments sweeter and more memorable.

items.name: Chocolate Cookies
items.description: Satisfy your cravings with our delectable Chocolate Cookies. A perfect balance of cocoa richness in every delightful, chewy bite.

items.name: Chocolate Summer Berries
items.description: Celebrate summer with Chocolate-Dipped Berries. Juicy, vibrant, and dipped in rich chocolate, a delightful fusion of flavors capturing the essence of the season.

items.name: Classic Cheesecake
items.description: Taste timeless perfection with our Classic Cheesecake. Creamy, velvety, and rich, it's a true indulgence that never goes out of style.

items.name: Cookies Cream Cake
items.description: Experience delight in every slice of our Cookies and Cream Cake. A perfect fusion of luscious creaminess and irresistible cookie crunch.

items.name: Easter Cupcakes
items.description: Celebrate Easter with our charming Easter Cupcakes. Adorned with festive designs, these cupcakes bring joy and sweetness to your holiday gatherings.

items.name: Fruit Cake
items.description: Savor the blend of ripe fruits in our sumptuous Fruit Cake. A timeless treat that embodies the essence of indulgence.

items.name: Isometric chocolate brownies
items.description: Experience perfection with our Isometric Chocolate Brownies. A harmonious blend of geometry and rich chocolate flavors, elevating your brownie enjoyment.

items.name: Monster Theme Cake
items.description: Unleash fun with our Monster Theme Cake. A whimsical creation that combines creativity and taste, perfect for celebrations full of excitement.

items.name: Muffin Devil Horns
items.description: Indulge in Muffin Devil Horns – a wickedly delicious treat. A playful twist on muffins that adds a touch of devilish delight.

items.name: Muffin Ghost
items.description: Enjoy Muffin Ghosts – a spooktacular delight. Soft muffins transformed into adorable ghostly treats, perfect for Halloween or any fun occasion.

items.name: Pumpkin Spice Cupcakes
items.description: Celebrate the season with our Pumpkin Spice Cupcakes. A delightful blend of warm spices and pumpkin flavor, a true autumn delight.
